headline: Why AMD Stock Is Plummeting Today
summary: Advanced Micro Devices (NASDAQ: AMD) stock saw a day of big sell-offs Thursday.  The semiconductor company's share price wound up down 8.4% in a day of trading that saw the S&P 500 fall 3.5% and the Nasdaq Composite fall 4.4%.  The stock market followed Wednesday's surge on tariff news with substantial sell-offs today as more information about import taxes on China came into focus.
